Placeholder — see apps/archon-sync-api/src/bundled-docs-routes.ts.

The sync-api serves plugin-authoring guides from this directory at
/api/v1/bundled-docs/*. Drop markdown files here to publish them in-app.
Empty directory is fine; the endpoint returns an empty list.

Path can be overridden via ARCHON_BUNDLED_DOCS_DIR env var.
